

# Simple example with a single compound
# no MDS options mentioned here



LAT                         <= triggers readin of new compound data

name     = dimer
file     = in/dimer.lat
elements = Fe Y

r0 = 1.5                    Desired bond distance in dimer
w_r0 = 0.0001               weight

Ec       = -0.123
u_Ec     = 0.0068           uncertainty (w and u can be freely mixed for different properties)


option: quench_always       Always scale velocities to 0.

